template.value:
Images must have a QR code present. Currently accepts .jpg, .png, and .tif

Note: If the image doesn't have EXIF data, then the timestamp must be included somewhere in the filename in the format YYYYMMDD-HHMMSS

Warning: Unlike the magic desktop folder, (as of now) your filename MUST be unique or else will overwrite in our system.
